<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US"><span style="">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The Apostle Paul is telling us something
similar when in his instructions to Timothy<b>,</b> he says the following<b>:</b>
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;" lang="EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>
</p>

